      "summary": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tCeres Open Data Index\n\t\n\nA curated, deduplicated index of 1,854,596 open datasets from 47 open data portals across ~25 countries plus international sources (EU Open Data Portal, HDX). This is the largest aggregated open data metadata index available as a single downloadable resource.\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\tDataset Description\n\t\n\nThis dataset contains normalized metadata from government and institutional open data portals. It was harvested by Ceres, a harvest-first toolkit for open data, via… See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/AndreaBozzo/ceres-open-data-index.",
